doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='Reusable participation-guide microsite for OGC code sprints. OS4CSAPI hosts the CSAPI community at the events.')
        meta(name='author', content='OS4CSAPI')

        title OS4CSAPI Code Sprint Guide

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
        link(rel='shortcut icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')
        link(rel='icon', type='image/png', sizes='192x192', href='assets/img/logos/os4csapi.png')
        link(rel='apple-touch-icon', href='assets/img/logos/os4csapi.png')

        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.3/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top
            .container
                a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top') OS4CSAPI · Sprint Guide
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.text-uppercase.ms-auto.py-4.py-lg-0
                        li.nav-item: a.nav-link(href='#events') Events
                        li.nav-item: a.nav-link(href='https://github.com/OS4CSAPI', target='_blank', rel='noopener') OS4CSAPI

        header.masthead
            .container
                .masthead-heading.text-uppercase OS4CSAPI Code Sprint Guide
                .masthead-subheading An open invitation to the CSAPI community at every OGC sprint.
                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl.text-uppercase(href='#events') See current events

        section.page-section#events
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase Current &amp; Upcoming Events
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted One participation guide per sprint. Live countdown, calendar, time zones, and the practical details.
                .row.g-4.justify-content-center
                    each ev in events
                        .col-md-7
                            .card.shadow-sm.h-100
                                .card-body
                                    h4.text-uppercase.mb-2
                                        a(href=`${ev.id}/`)= ev.title
                                    p.text-muted.fst-italic.mb-3= ev.subtitle
                                    p.small.mb-1
                                        i.fas.fa-map-marker-alt.text-primary.me-2
                                        | #{ev.venue.name} · #{ev.eventTimeZoneLabel}
                                    p.small.text-muted.mb-3
                                        i.fas.fa-calendar.text-primary.me-2
                                        | #{new Date(ev.startDateTimeISO).toUTCString().slice(0,16)} – #{new Date(ev.endDateTimeISO).toUTCString().slice(0,16)}
                                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.text-uppercase(href=`${ev.id}/`) Open guide

        section.page-section.bg-light#about
            .container
                .text-center
                    h2.section-heading.text-uppercase About OS4CSAPI
                    h3.section-subheading.text-muted Open Source for OGC API – Connected Systems.
                .row.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-9
                        p.text-center
                            | OS4CSAPI is a continuing initiative led from inside the OGC API Connected Systems Standards Working Group that aims to collaborate with open-source projects to advance shared goals around the CSAPI standard. These sprint guides are how we issue an open invitation: if you are working on CSAPI in the open during a sprint, you are an OS4CSAPI participant for that sprint. No formal membership; no required hours.

        footer.footer.py-4
            .container
                .row.align-items-center
                    .col-md-6.text-lg-start
                        | © OS4CSAPI 2026
                    .col-md-6.text-lg-end
                        a.link-light.me-3(href='https://github.com/OS4CSAPI', target='_blank', rel='noopener') OS4CSAPI org
                        a.link-light(href='https://github.com/OS4CSAPI/code-sprint-guide', target='_blank', rel='noopener') Source

        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js', crossorigin='anonymous')
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
